      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute gem! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it\u2019s still in breathtaking, flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been garage-kept, smoke-free, and drives like an absolute dream. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be so happy! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
