    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This example features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing for a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is routed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a GKN-viscous limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is superlative; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension maintains factory-spec damping with fresh OEM bushings, ensuring the original handling dynamics are preserved. The exterior presents with factory-original paint thickness and zero oxidation, while the cabin features Nappa leather with pristine bolsters and no delamination of the interior trim. This vehicle is mechanically synchronized and cosmetically flawless.",
